{"tid":2040535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日希慎大圍捕人士獲保釋後稱黑警沒收電話同八達通作證物用途","createTime":"2020-05-28T15:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T17:29:25.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68a541b74c7a001dbcc6c1f76374eda7e5928b17","tid":2040535,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"【5.28 被捕人獲准保釋｜重聚相擁】<br />\n<br />\n昨日警方於港九各區拘捕近400人。今日晚上11時左右，北角警署內被捕人士陸續獲批准保釋，現場警員以揚聲器宣布，因等待處理人數眾多，故此要作人流管制，暫時每五人一批獲准保釋。不少被捕人士獲保釋後，與家人重聚時相擁。<br />\n<br />\n其中一位昨日於銅鑼灣希慎廣場外被捕人士稱，警方以非法集結罪名將其拘捕，電話及八達通被沒收作證物，暫以$500保釋。<br />\n<br />\n現時北角警署外仍有數十名親友等候，區議員及社工在場協助。<br />\n<br />\n攝 Photo : Billy Choy<br />\n撰 Edit ：Billy Choy, Ivan Ng<br />\n<br />\n#flashmediahongkong #fmhk #flashmediahk #hkmedia #2020 #香港示威 #HKProtest #被捕人親友 #北角<br />\n<br />\nLike同Share本媒專頁Flash Media HongKong (FMHK) 以獲取更多新聞資訊和社會報導。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/flashmediahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fflashmediahk%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=18a799b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/flashmediahk/</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: @flashmediahk  @ North Point<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112467260231947/posts/170877201057619/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112467260231947%2Fposts%2F170877201057619%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=3e45813f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112467260231947/posts/170877201057619/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80effa870eae929aeae1a15f2488522be1e8388","tid":2040535,"uid":36073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3511ea738f53064fc1a84d36c8